
*******************
* How to run maya *
*******************

cd /netapp/backstage/pub/apps/renderman2/applications/linux/bin;
./rfm 2017 21.6;

rfm location:
/netapp/backstage/pub/bin/rfm -> /netapp/backstage/pub/apps/renderman2/applications/linux/bin/rfm

*******************************
* Where Maya module files are *
*******************************

/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/maya2/modules

************************************
* Where RenderMan header files are *
************************************

/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/renderman2/applications/linux/RenderManProServer-21.6/include

****************************************
* Where RenderMan plug-in examples are *
****************************************

/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/renderman2/applications/linux/PixarRenderMan-Examples-21.6_1803412-linuxRHEL6_gcc44icc150.x86_64/plugins

*************************************
* How to publish RenderMan plug-ins *
*************************************

[.so file path]
/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/renderman2/rfm-extensions/21.6/lib/RIS

[.args file path]
/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/renderman2/rfm-extensions/21.6/lib/RIS/Args

[source codes with its Makefile]
/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/renderman2/rfm-extensions/21.6/lib/work/RIS

(note)
1) A .arg file must not have any tab indentations. (space only!)
2) The 'nodeid' in a .arg file must be unique!
   You can find the nodeid list in /netapp/backstage/pub/apps/renderman2/rfm-extensions/21.6/NodeIDs.readme.

**********************************
* Where Houdini header files are *
**********************************

/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/houdini2/applications/linux/hfs16.5.268/toolkit/include

****************************************
* Where Houdini external libraries are *
****************************************

/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/houdini2/applications/linux/hfs16.5.268/dsolib

***********************************************
* How to check the OpenVDB version of Houdini *
***********************************************

/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/houdini2/applications/linux/hfs16.0.671/toolkit/include/openvdb/version.h
: 3.3.0

/netapp/backstage/pub/apps/houdini2/applications/linux/hfs16.5.268/toolkit/include/openvdb/version.h
: 4.0.1

